description:
Jovis is really enjoying being congratulated for his kindness. It all goes to his head, and he takes it upon himself to let everybody know how awesome he is, phoning the radio, writing to the newspaper and announcing it online.

Director: Mark Minors, Luke Manwaring
Starring: Joseph Cheetham-Wilkinson, Adrian Pace, Lydia Orange
